summary: Greg Andersen calls Julie D'Arcane to ask for help with his hacky sacks. The sacks have been up on the balcony since 1988.
suggested_actions: Confirm the time of Greg Andersen's visit to ensure Julie D'Arcane is prepared for his arrival.
Check if any additional assistance is needed for retrieving the hacky sacks from the balcony.
Follow up with Greg Andersen after the visit to ensure he successfully collected his hacky sacks and address any further concerns.
